caption.text:
Shopee: Melestarikan Warisan Budaya _ Plearn Herbal Cosmetics, Thailand

Dari buah kelapa sederhana, lahir harapan baru. Tong mengubah hasil panen lokal menjadi produk perawatan kecantikan alami, menciptakan kualitas hidup lebih baik bagi para petani di Samut Songkhram.

Saksikan “Shopee: Melestarikan Warisan Budaya” dan rayakan jutaan UMKM di seluruh Asia Tenggara, Taiwan dan Brasil yang terus tumbuh bersama Shopee, sambil menjaga keunikan budaya mereka.

-

From humble coconuts came new hope. Tong turned local harvests into natural beauty products, creating better livelihoods for farmers in Samut Songkhram.

Watch Shopee: Keeping Cultures Alive and celebrate the MSME sellers across Southeast Asia, Taiwan, and Brazil who have built their businesses while preserving their unique cultures.

#Shopee #Shopee10thBirthday #KeepingCulturesAlive

1. WAJIB FoIIow @shopee_id
2. LIKE & KOMEN Jawaban kamu di kolom komentar!
